                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 79vb: Who who donated it to the church of St. George so that it might be his guide to the Kingdom of Heaven. During the time of Täsfa Mikaʾel’s office. </q>
                           The donor is not mentioned, but it appears that the note refers to the name Wäldä Śǝllase mentioned in the concluding supplication. Besides, the note mentions Täsfa Mikaʾel, the head of St. George’s church. It is written in a secondary hand, the same which inserted the names of the donors in the supplication formulas.
